data.description: Welcome to 5167 Elba Drive, where comfort meets convenience in this inviting 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home. Step inside to find vinyl flooring seamlessly flowing throughout the living spaces and tile in the bathrooms. Enjoy chilly evenings by the fireplace in the spacious living area, creating a warm ambiance for relaxation.The heart of this home is its well-equipped kitchen boasting stainless steel appliances, perfect for culinary enthusiasts and family gatherings. Embrace eco-conscious living with solar panels adorning the roof, ensuring energy efficiency and sustainability.Conveniently located just two miles away from Tanger Outlets, shopping and grocery stores are within easy reach. The garage has been intelligently transformed into a versatile bonus room or 4th bedroom, cateringcatering to your evolving needs. Adjacent, discover a small office space, ideal for remote work or creative pursuits.  Outdoors, a delightful paver patio awaits, offering a perfect spot for outdoor dining or soaking up the sun. Two storage sheds provide ample space for your tools and outdoor gear, keeping your home organized and clutter-free.  With the added convenience of a wide, double driveway, parking is never a hassle. Don't miss the opportunity to call this charming North Charleston residence your home. Schedule a viewing today and embrace a lifestyle of comfort and ease.
